[{"id":"VH955609","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Two isolated, positively charged spheres are held together with an insulating string of negligible mass so that the centers of the spheres are a distance <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"L\"><math alttext=\"L\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>L</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> apart. Sphere 1 has charge <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Q sub 1\"><math alttext=\"Q sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><msub><mrow><mi>Q</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> and mass <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"M sub 1\"><math alttext=\"M sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><msub><mrow><mi>M</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> . Sphere 2 has charge <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2 Q sub 1\"><math alttext=\"2 Q sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mn>2</mn><mrow><msub><mrow><mi>Q</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> and mass <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2 M sub 1\"><math alttext=\"2 M sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><msub><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>M</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> . The two-sphere system has internal energy <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"U\"><math alttext=\"U\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>U</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> . What is the internal energy of the system after the string is cut and the spheres have moved far away from each other?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VH955609_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Zero</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the fraction U over 2\"><math alttext=\"the fraction U over 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mi>U</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfrac></mrow></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"U\"><math alttext=\"U\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>U</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">It cannot be determined unless an exact new distance between the spheres is given.</p>"],"answer":2}]